WEBVTT

00:06:57.583 --> 00:07:00.393
How to breathe in a room
with a person in pain.

00:07:00.417 --> 00:07:01.684
How to connect

00:07:01.708 --> 00:07:05.268
and build trust, no matter
the age, ability or illness.

00:07:05.292 --> 00:07:08.197
And how medical clowning
is an excellent way of using the arts

00:07:08.221 --> 00:07:10.768
to put the care back in health care.

00:07:10.792 --> 00:07:12.059
Thanks.

00:07:12.083 --> 00:07:15.708
(Applause)